		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi, I'm doing portraits and I would see if anyone can get an idea of ​​this aspect as it gets, think they are just photos with some filter?
<br />
<br /><img src="http://i288.photobucket.com/albums/ll171/torguen/vieja.png" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />know any program that can achieve this look by applying some filters?

		

