	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can achieve such result from a photo with halftone ordered dithering.
<br />
<br />It does not look like a handmade pixel art because of random pixels and jaggy lines, it would make no sense to place them this way if you draw it by hand.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


