		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can get similar looking pictures by bumping up the contrast of the image and reducing it to 4 colors. This can be done with Photoshop.
<br />
<br />For example:
<br /><img src="http://thefox.aspekt.fi/2bpp.png" alt="Image" />

		

